---
import ContentPage from '../layouts/ContentPage.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: `${SITE.url}/` },
  { name: 'Privacy Policy', url: `${SITE.url}/privacy/` },
];
---
<ContentPage
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Pool Shock Calculator handles data, analytics, cookies, and advertising."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <p><em>Last updated: {SITE.dataUpdated}.</em></p>

  <p>
    Pool Shock Calculator ({SITE.url}) respects your privacy. This policy explains
    what limited data we collect and how it’s used.
  </p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Calculator inputs stay in your browser.</strong> The pool volume, product, and readings you enter are used to compute your result on your device and are not sent to or stored on our servers.</li>
    <li><strong>Basic analytics.</strong> We may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand aggregate traffic, such as which pages are visited and general location and device type. This data is aggregated and not used to identify you.</li>
    <li><strong>Contact emails.</strong> If you email us, we keep your message and address only to respond and improve the tool.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Cookies and advertising</h2>
  <p>
    We may use cookies for analytics and, if advertising is enabled, to serve ads.
    Third-party ad and analytics providers may set their own cookies and use them,
    including for personalized advertising, subject to their policies. You can
    control cookies through your browser settings, and where required we’ll present
    a consent choice.
  </p>

  <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
  <p>
    Some product suggestions may be affiliate links, meaning we could earn a small
    commission if you buy through them, at no extra cost to you. Affiliate
    relationships never change the dose the calculator produces.
  </p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Use your browser’s controls to block or clear cookies.</li>
    <li>Opt out of personalized advertising through your ad settings or provider tools.</li>
    <li>Email us at <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a> with any privacy request.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>
    This site is intended for a general adult audience and is not directed at
    children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect their personal information.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this policy as the site evolves. Material changes will be reflected
    in the “last updated” date above.
  </p>
</ContentPage>
